title: More About Who?
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss if the Bills’ blowout of the Titans last night was more about the Bills or the Titans, exactly how good are the Eagles after beating the Vikings yesterday and their thoughts on the end of the NBA’s one-and-done rule.
